{
  "title": "Delicious Pressure-Cooked Australian Vialone-Nano Stew",
  "description": "This hearty stew showcases the unique texture and flavor of Vialone-Nano, paired with the convenience of pressure cooking. Perfect for a weeknight dinner or special occasion.",
  "cuisine": "australian",
